  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until lightly browned, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for an additional 1-2 minutes, until fragrant.",
    "Add the sambusa meat mix and cook, breaking up with a spoon, until browned and cooked through.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, salt, and black pepper and stir to combine.",
    "Add the cooked rice to the skillet and stir to combine with the meat mixture.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a serving platter and garnish with cilantro and habenero pepper slices.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with additional cilantro if desired."
